. **#Limit to event windows -- 10 years pre, 10 years post
. *Zimbabwe - CC IMPLEMENTATION IN 2000
. *Zimbabwe's 1979 independence constitution bookends the pre-treatment window.
. *Treatment event is CC implementation in 200, not a constitutional adoption.
. drop if year < 1990 & country == "Zimbabwe"
{txt}(35 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2010 & country == "Zimbabwe"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. 
. *ANGOLA - Two possible treatments: new const. in 1975 & 2010.
