{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1996 & country == "Philippines"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. *POLAND - New Const in 1997. Also had one in 1992 but not long lasting.
. drop if year < 1987 & country == "Poland"
{txt}(32 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2007 & country == "Poland"
{txt}(16 observations deleted)

{com}. *ROMANIA - TWO possible treatments: NEW CONST in 1965 and 1991.
. drop if year < 1955 & country == "Romania"
{txt}(0 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1975 & year < 1981 & country == "Romania"
{txt}(5 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Romania"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *RUSSIA - New Const. in 1993. Also new one in 1977 but windows overlap. Studying longer lasting one.
. drop if year < 1983 & country == "Russia"
{txt}(28 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2003 & country == "Russia"
{txt}(20 observations deleted)

{com}. *SERBIA - New Const. in 2006. 
. drop if year < 1996 & country == "Serbia"
{txt}(41 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2016 & country == "Serbia"
{txt}(7 observations deleted)

{com}. *SOLOMON ISLANDS - New Const. in 1978.
. drop if year < 1968 & country == "Solomon Islands"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1988 & country == "Solomon Islands"
{txt}(35 observations deleted)

{com}. *SPAIN - New Const. in 1978. Also new one in 1967 but windows overlap. Studying longer lasting one.
. drop if year < 1968 & country == "Spain"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1988 & country == "Spain"
{txt}(35 observations deleted)

{com}. *SRI LANKA - Many new Cons. but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1978.
. drop if year < 1968 & country == "Sri Lanka"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1988 & country == "Sri Lanka"
{txt}(35 observations deleted)

{com}. *SWEDEN - New Const. in 1974. 
. drop if year < 1964 & country == "Sweden"
{txt}(9 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1984 & country == "Sweden"
{txt}(39 observations deleted)

{com}. *SWITZERLAND - New Const. in 1999. 
. drop if year < 1989 & country == "Switzerland"
{txt}(34 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2009 & country == "Switzerland"
{txt}(14 observations deleted)

{com}. *TURKEY - New Const. in 1982. Also new Constitution in 1961. Not enough pre-treatment data. 
. drop if year < 1972 & country == "Turkey"
{txt}(17 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1992 & country == "Turkey"
{txt}(31 observations deleted)

{com}. *VANUATU - New Const in 1980.
. drop if year < 1970 & country == "Vanuatu"
{txt}(15 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1990 & country == "Vanuatu"
{txt}(33 observations deleted)

{com}. *VIETNAM - Many new Const but one lasts with enough pre/post treatment periods - 1992.
. drop if year < 1982 & country == "Vietnam"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2002 & country == "Vietnam"
{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. 
. 
. gen invest = csh_i*gdppc
{txt}(1,938 missing values generated)

{com}. **#Drop unusable donors (due to missing outcome data.)
. bysort c: egen miss = total(missing(invest))
{txt}
{com}. drop if miss > 0
{txt}(2,625 observations deleted)

{com}. drop miss
{txt}
{com}. 
. 
. **#Drop some that the code missed.
. drop if country == "Cyprus" /*Cyprus, new Const too early (1960). Not enough pretreatment data.*/
{txt}(69 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if country == "France" /*France, new Const too early (1958). Not enough pretreatment data.*/
{txt}(69 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if country == "Malaysia" /*Malaysia, new Const too early (1957). Not enough pretreatment data.*/
{txt}(69 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if country == "North Korea" /*North Korea, sparse predictor data. Outlier.*/
{txt}(0 observations deleted)

{com}. 
. 
. **#Create event time indicator, centered on event year
. *Nepals's treatment is CC implementation in 1975, not a constitutional adoption.
. *Clear syst-based coding for Nepal and manually set event year.
. gen event_year = year if syst == 1
{txt}(371 missing values generated)

{com}. replace event_year = . if country == "Nepal"
{txt}(0 real changes made)

{com}. replace event_year = 1975 if country == "Nepal" & year == 1975
{txt}(1 real change made)

{com}. 
. **#Coding blanks for those that had multiple events or events we are not considering.
. replace event_year = . if event_year == 1991 & country == "Albania"
{txt}(0 real changes made)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year != 1982 & country == "China"
{txt}(2 real changes made, 2 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year != 1975 & country == "Greece"
{txt}(2 real changes made, 2 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year != 2010 & country == "Kyrgyz Republic"
{txt}(2 real changes made, 2 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year == 1992 & country == "Mongolia"
{txt}(1 real change made, 1 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year == 1987 & country == "Philippines"
{txt}(1 real change made, 1 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year != 1997 & country == "Poland"
{txt}(1 real change made, 1 to missing)

{com}. replace event_year = . if event_year == 1972 & country == "Sri Lanka"
{txt}(1 real change made, 1 to missing)

{com}. 
. xtset c year
{res}
{col 1}{txt:Panel variable: }{res:c}{txt: (unbalanced)}
{p 1 16 2}{txt:Time variable: }{res:year}{txt:, }{res:{bind:1964}}{txt: to }{res:{bind:2021}}{txt:, but with a gap}{p_end}
{txt}{col 10}Delta: {res}1 unit
{txt}
{com}. gen event_time = 0  if event_year != .
{txt}(380 missing values generated)

{com}. replace event_time = 1  if l1.event_year != .
{txt}(19 real changes made)

{com}. replace event_time = 2  if l2.event_year != .
{txt}(19 real changes made)

{com}. replace event_time = 3  if l3.event_year != .
