. **#Limit to event windows -- 10 years pre, 10 years post
. *NAMIBIA - CC IMPLEMENTATION IN 2010
. *Namibia's 1990 independence constitution bookends the pre-treatment window.
. *Treatment event is CC implementation in 2010, not a constitutional adoption.
. drop if year < 2000 & country == "Namibia"
{txt}(45 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2020 & country == "Namibia"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. 
. *ANGOLA - Two possible treatments: new const. in 1975 & 2010.
. *1975 has v-dem data, but is missing potential predictor data, so will likely have to be dropped eventually.
. drop if year < 1965 & country == "Angola"
{txt}(10 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1985 & year < 2000 & country == "Angola"
{txt}(14 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2020 & country == "Angola"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. *BENIN - Many new Constitutions but only 1990 one is long lasting.
. drop if year < 1980 & country == "Benin"
{txt}(25 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2000 & country == "Benin"
{txt}(23 observations deleted)

{com}. *BOTSWANA - New Const. in 1966.
. drop if year < 1956 & country == "Botswana"
{txt}(1 observation deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1976 & country == "Botswana"
{txt}(47 observations deleted)

{com}. *BURUNDI - Many new Constitutions but 2004/2005 one lasts the longest. 2004 is interim and 2005 is new, use 2004 as event date.
. *Burundi's Constituion in 1974 and 1981 were both suspended within 10 years.
. *Their 1992 one was replaced with in interim one in 1998.
. drop if year < 1994 & country == "Burundi"
{txt}(39 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2014 & country == "Burundi"
{txt}(9 observations deleted)

{com}. *CAMEROON - New Const in 1972 that was long lasting. Also has new Consts in 1960 and 1961, ignoring due to overlap.
. drop if year < 1962 & country == "Cameroon"
{txt}(7 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1982 & country == "Cameroon"
{txt}(41 observations deleted)

{com}. *CAPE VERDE - New Const in 1980.
. drop if year < 1970 & country == "Cape Verde"
{txt}(15 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1990 & country == "Cape Verde"
{txt}(33 observations deleted)

{com}. *CHAD - Many new Const. but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods to study - 1996.
. drop if year < 1986 & country == "Chad"
{txt}(31 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2006 & country == "Chad"
{txt}(17 observations deleted)

{com}. *COMOROS - Many new Const. but only two are long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1978 & 2001.
. *Could also consider 2018 but short post-window. Ignoring for now.
. drop if year < 1968 & country == "Comoros"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1988 & year < 1991 & country == "Comoros"
{txt}(2 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2011 & country == "Comoros"
{txt}(12 observations deleted)

{com}. *CONGO - Many new Const. but only two are long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1979 and 2001.
. *Could also consider 2016 Const. for CAF treatment when post-window is shorter. Ignoring for now.
. drop if year < 1969 & country == "Congo"
{txt}(14 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1989 & year < 1991 & country == "Congo"
{txt}(1 observation deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2011 & country == "Congo"
{txt}(12 observations deleted)

{com}. *COTE D'IVOIRE - Three new Const. but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 2000.
. *Should also/instead consider 2016 Const. for CAF treatment when post-window is shorter. Ignoring here.
. drop if year < 1990 & country == "Cote d'Ivoire"
{txt}(35 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2010 & country == "Cote d'Ivoire"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. *EQUATORIAL GUINEA - Many new Const. but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1991.
. drop if year < 1981 & country == "Equatorial Guinea"
{txt}(26 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Equatorial Guinea"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *ERITREA - New Const. in 1997.
. drop if year < 1987 & country == "Eritrea"
{txt}(32 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2007 & country == "Eritrea"
{txt}(16 observations deleted)

{com}. *ETHIOPIA - Many new Const but only one are long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1994.
. *The 1976 Constitution is also long lasting (11 years) but its post-treatment period would overlap 1994's pre-period.
. drop if year < 1984 & country == "Ethiopia"
{txt}(29 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2004 & country == "Ethiopia"
{txt}(19 observations deleted)

{com}. *GABON - Many new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1991.
. *There is one in 1975 that is long lasting but its window overlaps with 1991.
. drop if year < 1981 & country == "Gabon"
{txt}(26 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Gabon"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *GAMBIA - Many new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1996.
. *We also consider 1970 Const but it is suspended in 1981, one year after window. We keep it here.
. drop if year < 1960 & country == "Gambia"
{txt}(5 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1980 & year < 1986 & country == "Gambia"
{txt}(5 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2006 & country == "Gambia"
{txt}(17 observations deleted)

{com}. *GUINEA - Two new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1990.
. *GUINEA second adoption in 2010 was replaced within a ten year window.
. drop if year < 1980 & country == "Guinea"
{txt}(25 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2000 & country == "Guinea"
{txt}(23 observations deleted)

{com}. *GUINEA-BISSAU - Two new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1984. Ignore 1973.
. drop if year < 1974 & country == "Guinea-Bissau"
{txt}(19 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1994 & country == "Guinea-Bissau"
{txt}(29 observations deleted)

{com}. *LESOTHO - Many new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1993.
. drop if year < 1983 & country == "Lesotho"
{txt}(28 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2003 & country == "Lesotho"
{txt}(20 observations deleted)

{com}. *LIBERIA - New Const in 1986.
. drop if year < 1976 & country == "Liberia"
{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1996 & country == "Liberia"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. *MADAGASCAR - Many new Const. but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 2010.
. drop if year < 2000 & country == "Madagascar"
{txt}(45 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2020 & country == "Madagascar"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. *MALAWI - New Const in 1994; two others in 1964/1966 that are close together.
. *We also consider 1966 because this is long lasting and fits in window.
. drop if year < 1956 & country == "Malawi"
{txt}(1 observation deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1976 & year < 1984 & country == "Malawi"
{txt}(7 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2004 & country == "Malawi"
{txt}(19 observations deleted)

{com}. *MALI - New Const in 1992.
. *Another in 1974 but this overlaps with pre-treatment period of next event. Other events in 2020/2023 that we are ignoring.
. drop if year < 1982 & country == "Mali"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2002 & country == "Mali"
{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. *MAURITANIA - Many new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods - 1991.
. drop if year < 1981 & country == "Mauritania"
{txt}(26 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Mauritania"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *MAURITIUS - New Const in 1968.
. drop if year < 1958 & country == "Mauritius"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1978 & country == "Mauritius"
{txt}(45 observations deleted)

{com}. *MOZAMBIQUE - Many new Const but only one is long lasting with enough post-treatment data - 2004.
. *Could potentially include 1990 but this overlaps pre/post period of 2004 event.
. drop if year < 1994 & country == "Mozambique"
{txt}(39 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2014 & country == "Mozambique"
{txt}(9 observations deleted)

{com}. *NIGER - Many new Const but only 2009/2010 is long lasting. 2009 AND 2010 represent new Const. Use 2009 as event year.
. drop if year < 1999 & country == "Niger"
{txt}(44 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2019 & country == "Niger"
{txt}(4 observations deleted)

{com}. *SAO TOME AND PRINCIPE - New Const in 1975.
. drop if year < 1965 & country == "Sao Tome and Principe"
{txt}(10 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1985 & country == "Sao Tome and Principe"
{txt}(38 observations deleted)

{com}. *SENEGAL - New Const in 2001.
. *Also had new Const in early 60's but not enough pre-treatment data.
. drop if year < 1991 & country == "Senegal"
{txt}(36 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2011 & country == "Senegal"
{txt}(12 observations deleted)

{com}. *SIERRA LEONE - New Const in 1996. This is really 1991 Const but it was not stably implemented until 1996. Use 1996 as event year.
. drop if year < 1986 & country == "Sierra Leone"
{txt}(31 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2006 & country == "Sierra Leone"
{txt}(17 observations deleted)

{com}. *SOMALIA - Two potential events: 1979 and 2012. Ignoring 2004 interim.
. drop if year < 1969 & country == "Somalia"
{txt}(14 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1989 & year < 2002 & country == "Somalia"
{txt}(12 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2022 & country == "Somalia"
{txt}(1 observation deleted)

