{com}. /*
> *Drop panels that have missing covariate data.
> *For non-outcome predictors, it only matters if pre-treatment data is available.
> *Creating pre-treatment averages so we avoid dropping those that have some data.
> */
> 
> destring length, replace;
{txt}length: all characters numeric; {res}replaced {txt}as {res}long
{txt}(185 missing values generated)
{res}{txt}
