. 
. *Event window for Nepal:
. *Implemented counter-corruption commission in 1975 - this is treatment year
. drop if year < 1965 & country == "Nepal"
{txt}(10 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1985 & country == "Nepal"
{txt}(38 observations deleted)

{com}. 
. *ALBANIA - TWO possible treatments: NEW CONST in 1976 and 1998.
. *To be consistent, since the 1998 one is long lasting we should include it but note that there are events in the pre-treatment period.
. drop if year < 1966 & country == "Albania"
{txt}(11 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1986 & year < 1988 & country == "Albania"
{txt}(1 observation deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2008 & country == "Albania"
{txt}(15 observations deleted)

{com}. *BANGLADESH - NEW CONST in 1986, technically a reinstatement but it is long lasting.
. drop if year < 1976 & country == "Bangladesh"
{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1996 & country == "Bangladesh"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. *BULGARIA - Two possible treatments: new const. in 1971 & 1991. Two close together for windows. Will use second as it is longer lasting.
. drop if year < 1981 & country == "Bulgaria"
{txt}(26 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Bulgaria"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *CHINA - Three new Const from 1975-1982, but only 1982 is long lasting with enough post-treatment periods.
. drop if year < 1972 & country == "China"
{txt}(17 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1992 & country == "China"
{txt}(31 observations deleted)

{com}. *CZECH REPUBLIC - NEW CONST in 1993.
. drop if year < 1983 & country == "Czech Republic"
{txt}(28 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2003 & country == "Czech Republic"
{txt}(20 observations deleted)

{com}. *GERMAN DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC - NEW CONST in 1968
. drop if year < 1958 & country == "German Democratic Republic"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1978 & country == "German Democratic Republic"
{txt}(45 observations deleted)

{com}. *GREECE - NEW CONST in 1975 that is long lasting. Many before then.
. drop if year < 1965 & country == "Greece"
{txt}(10 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1985 & country == "Greece"
{txt}(38 observations deleted)

{com}. *HUNGARY - NEW CONST in 2011.
. drop if year < 2001 & country == "Hungary"
{txt}(46 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2021 & country == "Hungary"
{txt}(2 observations deleted)

{com}. *KYRGYZ REPUBLIC - NEW CONST in 2010.
. drop if year < 2000 & country == "Kyrgyz Republic"
{txt}(45 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2020 & country == "Kyrgyz Republic"
{txt}(3 observations deleted)

{com}. *LAOS - NEW CONST in 1991.
. drop if year < 1981 & country == "Laos"
{txt}(26 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Laos"
{txt}(22 observations deleted)

{com}. *MONGOLIA - NEW CONST in 1990, interim but permanent one in 1992 that lasted so use 1990 as event year.
. *Also new Const in 1960 but not enough pre-treatment data.
. drop if year < 1980 & country == "Mongolia"
{txt}(25 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2000 & country == "Mongolia"
{txt}(23 observations deleted)

{com}. *MYANMAR - TWO possible treatments: NEW CONST in 1974 and 2008.
. drop if year < 1964 & country == "Myanmar"
{txt}(9 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1984 & year < 1998 & country == "Myanmar"
{txt}(13 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2018 & country == "Myanmar"
{txt}(5 observations deleted)

{com}. *PHILIPPINES - New Const in 1986/1987. 1986 is interim, 1987 is new and long lasting.
. *Also has a new Const. in 1973 but overlaps with this post/pre treatment window. Ignoring here.
. drop if year < 1976 & country == "Philippines"
{txt}(21 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1996 & country == "Philippines"
{txt}(27 observations deleted)

{com}. *POLAND - New Const in 1997. Also had one in 1992 but not long lasting.
. drop if year < 1987 & country == "Poland"
{txt}(32 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2007 & country == "Poland"
{txt}(16 observations deleted)

{com}. *ROMANIA - TWO possible treatments: NEW CONST in 1965 and 1991.
. drop if year < 1955 & country == "Romania"
{txt}(0 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 1975 & year < 1981 & country == "Romania"
{txt}(5 observations deleted)

{com}. drop if year > 2001 & country == "Romania"
