. 
. **#Create event time indicator, centered on event year
. *Namibia's treatment is CC implementation in 2010, not a constitutional adoption.
. *Clear syst-based coding for Namibia and manually set event year.
. gen event_year = year if syst == 1
{txt}(2,693 missing values generated)

{com}. replace event_year = . if country == "Namibia"
{txt}(0 real changes made)

{com}. replace event_year = 2010 if country == "Namibia" & year == 2010
{txt}(1 real change made)

{com}. 
